- Katie, they're teenagers,
this is what teenagers do,

52:53.045 --> 52:54.712
we can't blame it all on Sam.

52:54.755 --> 52:56.547
- Lauren wanted to
invite Milo over,

52:56.591 --> 52:58.799
but didn't have the
guts to invite just him,

52:58.843 --> 53:00.593
