- Why are you talking
to my sister like that?

55:02.008 --> 55:03.674
- It's not my fault
your sister's so easy.

55:05.511 --> 55:07.594
- Why don't you just leave
her alone, all right?

55:07.638 --> 55:10.723
- Security, hey, there's a
fight happening over there,

55:10.766 --> 55:11.807
those two kids.

55:14.854 --> 55:16.895
- Yo, none of us buy that
innocent act anymore.

55:16.939 --> 55:17.688
She's a freak.

55:19.400 --> 55:20.482
She likes it rough.

55:21.277 --> 55:22.943
- Yeah, ha.

55:22.987 --> 55:23.902
- Yo, what the--
Whoa, whoa, whoa,

55:23.946 --> 55:25.029
whoa, relax, relax.

55:25.072 --> 55:26.363
I saw that, I saw
that, I saw that,

55:26.407 --> 55:27.323
- Yeah, he saw it.
- Let's go, Tommy.

55:27.366 --> 55:29.074
- Relax, relax.
- I'm sorry.

55:29.118 --> 55:30.743
Yeah, not so pretty
