55:37.084 --> 55:38.709
- You guys are home late.

55:38.753 --> 55:39.960
What's up?

55:40.004 --> 55:42.296
- I don't wanna talk about it.

55:42.340 --> 55:44.214
- Are they always this moody?

55:45.551 --> 55:46.342
- No,

55:47.428 --> 55:48.177
