56:01.108 --> 56:01.857
Hey,

56:03.944 --> 56:05.611
what's going on?

56:05.654 --> 56:06.362
- Nothing.

56:08.449 --> 56:10.657
- It's okay, is it
something at school?

56:11.660 --> 56:13.118
(Lauren sighs)

56:13.162 --> 56:14.995
We can talk about it, I
promise we can fix this.

56:15.039 --> 56:16.705
- No, we can't.

56:16.749 --> 56:19.291
