that Milo liked me,

56:29.804 --> 56:33.639
that he wanted to get
to know me better,

56:33.682 --> 56:37.810
and that I should have
him up in my room,

56:39.522 --> 56:43.190
and we started kissing,
and I wasn't ready,

56:43.234 --> 56:45.234
and then things got aggressive.

56:45.277 --> 56:48.070
- Sweetheart, this
is not your fault.

56:48.114 --> 56:50.197
- Yes, it is.

56:50.241 --> 56:52.741
And he's got a picture of me.

56:52.785 --> 56:53.992
I don't know how he took it,

56:54.036 --> 56:56.078
but he sent it to
all of his friends,

56:56.122 --> 56:57.996
and now everyone thinks
I had sex with him.

56:59.417 --> 57:02.626
And the thing is, is
I really liked him.

57:06.048 --> 57:07.840
- (sighs) Oh, honey.

57:07.883 --> 57:11.552
Milo was trying to take
advantage of you, okay?

57:11.595 --> 57:12.928
You didn't do anything wrong.

57:13.889 --> 57:15.347
Come here, sweetheart.

57:15.391 --> 57:16.890
Oh.

57:16.934 --> 57:18.976
