57:20.604 --> 57:21.353
- Thanks, Mom.

57:23.399 --> 57:25.983
(Katie sighs)

57:28.946 --> 57:31.238
Katie: So, what
happened with you?

57:38.622 --> 57:40.372
- Mom, I'm sorry, but,

57:42.543 --> 57:44.918
I got suspended for punching
Milo Venetta in the face.

57:46.839 --> 57:47.838
- Wow.

57:49.842 --> 57:53.677
Well, punching someone
is never a good idea,

57:54.889 --> 57:58.223
but I think I understand
why you did it.

57:59.935 --> 58:01.477
- Yeah?

58:01.520 --> 58:03.770
- Lauren told me what happened.

58:03.814 --> 58:05.731
- He had a picture of her.

58:05.774 --> 58:07.107
He showed it around like,

58:07.151 --> 58:09.359
like it was some
trophy or something.

58:09.403 --> 58:10.736
